profile:
Based out of the Okanagan in West Kelowna BC, JTech Drafting provides residential design and drafting services to clients all over Western Canada.  We can provide conceptual drawings and renderings, development permits, building permits, for garages, basement developments, home renovations, low-density multifamily projects, inner city redevelopment projects to new custom-built homes. 
JTech can assist you with getting a great start on your next project.  We are the first step in making your vision a reality.
